nodes.text: Dunn was a male Human who was a supply sergeant in the Imperial Army of the Sith Empire. He was stationed in the city of Sobrik on the planet Balmorra during the Cold War.

Supply Sergeant Dunn appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as an Equipment Commendations for Imperial players on Balmorra. With the release of Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015, he was removed from the game along with the rest of the Equipment Commendations Vendors.
